169
00:14:52,017 --> 00:14:53,560
It's been a long time...

170
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:58,398
How many years has it been
since you returned to the village?

171
00:15:04,029 --> 00:15:05,155
Kakashi...

172
00:15:08,825 --> 00:15:10,535
