173
00:15:12,579 --> 00:15:14,581
It was an understandable
decision of the Third Hokage

174
00:15:14,664 --> 00:15:18,460
who appointed you to the role
of watching over Naruto...

175
00:15:19,044 --> 00:15:20,337
But even at your level,

176
00:15:20,420 --> 00:15:23,882
