to this village sooner or later.

181
00:15:40,398 --> 00:15:44,361
All told, at first I was concerned
only about him, but...

182
00:15:46,529 --> 00:15:47,656
What is it?

183
00:15:48,406 --> 00:15:50,825
The guy joined an organization.

184
00:15:52,202 --> 00:15:53,411
An organization?

185
00:15:55,413 --> 00:15:57,499
