Until recently,
they weren't making any dramatic moves

189
00:16:09,761 --> 00:16:11,888
except some cloak-and-dagger activities.

190
00:16:11,971 --> 00:16:14,224
The biggest concern is
the members of that organization.

191
00:16:14,974 --> 00:16:18,103
Almost all of them are
listed on the Bingo Book,

192
00:16:18,186 --> 00:16:22,524
all S-rank deviant criminals.

193
00:16:23,608 --> 00:16:27,070
That Itachi is among them.

194
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:30,865
If the nine of them get together,

195
00:16:30,949 --> 00:16:33,576
