you already know what it means.

197
00:16:42,544 --> 00:16:47,006
But recently,
Orochimaru pulled out of the organization.

198
00:16:47,090 --> 00:16:48,758
And at that time,

199
00:16:48,842 --> 00:16:52,137
other members of the organization
went in to action in different areas,

200
00:16:52,220 --> 00:16:54,472
in pairs gathering Jutsu and things.

201
00:16:55,473 --> 00:16:58,435
Is there proof that one of those
things is the Nine-Tailed Fox?

202
00:16:59,352 --> 00:17:01,896
It's possible.

203
00:17:02,814 --> 00:17:06,901
Because it's one of the spirits
who possess the strongest Chakra...

204
00:17:09,487 --> 00:17:10,572
Kakashi...

205
00:17:10,655 --> 00:17:12,741
Sooner or later,

206
00:17:12,824 --> 00:17:16,035
that Naruto will have to
live watching his back...

207
