That's his destiny.

208
00:17:23,710 --> 00:17:26,463
For now, you should keep
your eyes on Sasuke.

209
00:17:27,338 --> 00:17:30,467
It's necessary for you to teach
him how to use his Sharingan.

210
00:17:31,426 --> 00:17:35,221
I'll take care of Naruto for a while.

211
00:17:41,895 --> 00:17:46,441
