Naruto is your target?

212
00:17:49,444 --> 00:17:53,865
I know that you two aren't
the only ones on the move...

213
00:17:55,492 --> 00:17:59,370
The name of your organization
is Akatsuki, right?

214
00:18:02,457 --> 00:18:03,500
Akatsuki?

215
00:18:04,167 --> 00:18:06,961
Kisame! We'll take Kakashi.

216
00:18:07,045 --> 00:18:09,047
Erase the other two.

217
00:18:12,842 --> 00:18:15,428
Severe Leaf Hurricanes!

218
00:18:26,147 --> 00:18:27,148
