219
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:31,861
The Leaf's noble, blue fierce animal...

220
00:18:32,821 --> 00:18:34,322
Mighty Guy!

221
00:18:35,031 --> 00:18:36,866
What a sight...

222
00:18:36,950 --> 00:18:38,535
Shouldn't you be called a strange beast?

223
00:18:39,577 --> 00:18:41,037
Don't underestimate that man...

224
00:18:41,788 --> 00:18:43,998
That man is Itachi!

225
00:18:53,299 --> 00:18:54,926
You did this to Kakashi...?

226
00:18:55,593 --> 00:18:57,929
Don't look at Itachi's eyes, Guy!

227
00:18:58,012 --> 00:18:59,389
You'll be caught up in his Jutsu!

228
00:18:59,806 --> 00:19:02,475
