229
00:19:02,559 --> 00:19:04,519
In order to fight Kakashi,

230
00:19:04,602 --> 00:19:07,355
I devised ways to battle the Sharingan.

231
00:19:09,941 --> 00:19:11,776
Open your eyes, both of you!

232
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:14,237
B-But...

233
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:16,364
When you battle with the Sharingan,

234
00:19:16,447 --> 00:19:18,533
it's not a problem if
you don't look at those eyes!

235
00:19:19,117 --> 00:19:21,244
