you're probably right, but...

238
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:31,629
You're the only one who can do that.

239
00:19:32,005 --> 00:19:33,006
That's true...

240
00:19:33,715 --> 00:19:36,593
There's a knack to reading all
of your opponents' movements

241
00:19:36,676 --> 00:19:37,802
only by his feet.

242
00:19:37,886 --> 00:19:40,471
But I can't teach it to
you in this emergency.

243
00:19:40,555 --> 00:19:42,557
Just get used it right now!

244
00:19:44,225 --> 00:19:45,268
What should we do?

245
00:19:45,351 --> 00:19:47,770
Kurenai, get Kakashi to the medical team.

246
00:19:48,897 --> 00:19:51,524
-Asuma, you are my back-up!
-Okay!

247
00:19:53,318 --> 00:19:58,031
And until the reinforcements of
Anbu Black Ops I arranged for arrive,

248
00:19:58,114 --> 00:20:00,575
