Interesting... That's some nerve...

250
00:20:05,163 --> 00:20:07,749
Kisame... Pull the plug.

251
00:20:08,333 --> 00:20:10,960
We didn't come to have a war.

252
00:20:11,044 --> 00:20:13,588
It's too bad,
but no more of this nonsense.

253
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:15,465
We're leaving.

254
00:20:16,716 --> 00:20:19,344
Too bad... I was finally feeling motivated.

255
00:20:20,428 --> 00:20:22,096
It can't be helped.

256
00:20:35,109 --> 00:20:36,277
All right!

257
00:20:46,079 --> 00:20:48,081
Here I go!

258
00:20:49,832 --> 00:20:52,293
Y-You're putting too much spirit into it.

259
00:20:52,377 --> 00:20:56,965
You're not training on a mountain retreat,
you know that, right?

260
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:13,314
A cycle of hardship, right?

261
00:21:14,273 --> 00:21:18,277
Inside, we were crying, right?

262
00:21:19,529 --> 00:21:24,701
But the one thing we won't give up

263
00:21:24,784 --> 00:21:27,328
is the dream we've chosen, right?

264
00:21:28,329 --> 00:21:30,623
It's a secondary role,

265
00:21:33,292 --> 00:21:36,671
a role in the shadows

266
00:21:36,754 --> 00:21:41,551
But in reaching for that dream,

267
00:21:41,884 --> 00:21:47,473
let us stay centered, let us stay true

268
00:21:47,557 --> 00:21:52,228
Over and over,
we hung on without giving up

269
00:21:52,562 --> 00:21:56,941
Over and over, we kept coming back up

270
00:21:57,400 --> 00:22:01,738
Over and over,

271
00:22:01,821 --> 00:22:07,076
we believed and dreamed

272
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:12,665
Over and over, we've seen fools

273
00:22:12,749 --> 00:22:18,046
Over and over,
we've stood in the shadows of others

274
00:22:19,630 --> 00:22:22,175
Now, it's our turn...

275
00:22:22,258 --> 00:22:27,889
Let us bask in our dreams

276
00:22:38,775 --> 00:22:41,069
There's a super beautiful
young lady over there!

277
00:22:41,152 --> 00:22:42,570
She just winked at us!

278
00:22:42,653 --> 00:22:45,406
Look, Naruto!
She must be interested in us!

279
00:22:45,698 --> 00:22:47,408
She may be cuter than Sakura!

280
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:49,494
– All right, Naruto!
– Yeah!

281
00:22:49,577 --> 00:22:51,704
Go back, train, then go to bed.

282
00:22:51,788 --> 00:22:54,624
You always do that to me!

283
00:22:54,707 --> 00:22:59,962
Next time: "Jiraiya:
Naruto's Potential Disaster!"

284
00:23:00,046 --> 00:23:02,423
What are we gonna do about my training?!

